title: Oleta Adams - Circle of One (1990) RESEED
description:
MP3/256Kbps

After a successful collaboration with Tears for Fears on their The Seeds of Love album, Oleta Adams was offered a record deal. Circle of One received much critical acclaim and even peaked at #1 on the UK album chart. The album was certified Gold in the United States and spawned two Grammy nominations. Beautiful songs and rich in voice, it&#039;s her best.

Recorded at Real World Studios, 1990
Produced by Roland Orzabal and Dave Bascombe
